summary: This document appears to be a confidential communication from AT&T regarding the inability to obtain location information for a specific mobile number. It discusses potential reasons for the lack of data and emphasizes caution in using the provided location records for investigative purposes.
keyFacts: The document indicates that location information could not be obtained due to the mobile being powered off, out of service area, or in an area where location information is not available.
AT&T provides a confidence level and details about the data source used for location tracking.
The document warns that location data may not be exact due to sourcing from various databases.
